OL,7,FStarmer confirmed he held a Cabinet
OL,8,Fmeeting on this issue on Tuesday
OL,9,Fmorning, adding: "I think it's really
OL,10,Fimportant that we indicate to voters
OL,11,Fthat we get it. I think we need to
OL,12,Fexplain the decisions we've taken - we
OL,13,Fhad to stop the chaos, we had to
OL,14,Fstabilise the economy."
OL,16,FThe PM did not answer questions on
OL,17,Fwhether he is re-thinking the policy
