OL,7,FCabinet minister Wes Streeting earlier
OL,8,Fadmitted to ITV News that the policy
OL,9,Fwas a "big issue" at the ballot box
OL,10,Flast week but said there was no formal
OL,11,Freview taking place, despite reports.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News: "I'm not going to
OL,14,Finsult your viewers by pretending
OL,15,Fwinter fuel hasn't been a big issue on
OL,16,Fthe doorstep, it has... And at the
OL,17,Fballot box, there's no doubt about
OL,18,Fthat."
