OL,7,FThe Guardian reported on Monday that
OL,8,Fwhile a full restoration of the
OL,9,Funiversal winter fuel payment was
OL,10,Funlikely, the government was
OL,11,Fconsidering whether to increase the
OL,12,F#11,500 threshold over which
OL,13,Fpensioners are no longer eligible for
OL,14,Fthe allowance.
OL,16,FBut such a move has been rejected by
OL,17,FDowning Street, partly because the
OL,18,Fpayment is now aligned with
OL,19,Feligibility for pension credit and
OL,20,Fwidening access to that would wipe out
OL,21,Fany savings from the policy.
